             was indicted for <rs id="t18290115-144-off753" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18290115-144-off753" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18290115-144-off753" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18290115-144-cd754" type="crimeDate">19th of December</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18290115-144-off753 t18290115-144-cd754"></join>, 1 watch, value 1l., and 1 seal, value 10s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18290115-144-victim1120" type="victimName">
                     Charles 
                     Gracie
                  <interp inst="t18290115-144-victim1120" type="surname" value="Gracie"></interp>
